I acknowledge that you've provided a code: FOXTROT_HOTEL_2468.

However, I should let you know that I don't retain information between separate conversations. Each time we interact, I start fresh without memory of previous exchanges. So while I'm noting this code now for use within our current conversation, it won't be available to me in future conversations unless you provide it again.
